      "description": "Looking for an affordable entry point or a fixer-upper project? This vehicle is priced to move and offers a real opportunity for the budget-conscious or mechanically inclined buyer! We'll be upfront \u2014 this car is in poor condition, with noticeable wear inside and out, some mechanical issues that will need attention, and cosmetic imperfections throughout. It's not a daily driver for everyone, but at this price, it could be a great project, a parts car, or a stepping stone. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises, just honest value!",
