    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition \u2014 and we want to be completely upfront with you about what that means. The exterior shows significant wear, including noticeable rust, dents, and paint that has faded and peeled in multiple areas. The interior has seen better days, with worn and torn upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general deterioration throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car has known issues that will require attention and repair before it can be considered fully reliable \u2014 buyers should budget for additional work beyond the purchase price. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, a hobbyist looking for a project vehicle, or someone seeking parts. There are no illusions here: this car needs work, but it does represent an opportunity at the right price for the right buyer.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in poor condition, and we want buyers to have a clear picture before inquiring. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect noticeable dents, scratches, and paint fading or peeling in multiple areas. The interior has seen better days, with worn or torn upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general signs of heavy use. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will require attention; it is best suited for a buyer comfortable with repair work or someone looking for a project vehicle or parts source. There are no major hidden surprises beyond what is described \u2014 what you see is what you get. This is priced accordingly to reflect its current state, making it an opportunity for the right buyer willing to invest time and money into bringing it back.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
